headline: Here's How Many Shares of VICI Properties You Should Own to Get $5,000 in Yearly Dividends
summary: Investing in dividend stocks is a great way to make a lot of passive income each year.  Many high-quality companies pay high-yielding dividends, enabling you to generate more passive income from every dollar you invest.  VICI Properties (NYSE: VICI) has been a great income investment over the years.
